Update order creation to consolidate cart items into a single order

Refactors the order creation process from handling individual cart items to consolidating them into a single order with a combined total price. Updates the `Order` entity and `CreateOrderDto` to support `productId`, `selectedSize`, and `cartItems` for this consolidated order structure.

